concept.title: Real users
concept.aboutDescription: A small non-profit organization. Help us to avoid fake profiles. Soon, you will like the photos or the profile of a user. The concept of the app is to find yourself with a smile in an activity. Participate or share to socialize!

concept.title: Never alone
concept.aboutDescription: Meeting friends, having fun and talking to everyone, about everything, and in all languages, it's always easier with an application that translates everything automatically. The language barrier no longer exists, it's time to get together to enjoy an unforgettable social life

concept.title: Locals and internationals
concept.aboutDescription: The first friendly dating app to help internationals and organizers find each other and socialize. Soon geolocated and shared with maps and notifications so you don't forget anything. A bit of patience. It's time to participate or share...

concept.title: Private address
concept.aboutDescription: A simple picnic, an evening at home, a sports session, a cinema, a visit to a museum, a cultural trip, a concert, a meal, ... there are many themes to meet more people , just participate or share activities with SOCIALIZUS!

concept.title: Create activities
concept.aboutDescription:
The objective of the application is also to help the organizers who do it for fun or to earn a living, they must be respected. We will help them without ever asking them to pay or become a promoter. 
 Share or participate in the SOCIALIZUS project

concept.title: Coming soon
concept.aboutDescription: With an association everything is much slower. We will quickly offer messaging and other options to invite your friends, people you have already met or liked. Share or participate in the Socializus project. Help us grow the community
